<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
    <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light dark">
    <title>Orden Cancelada</title>
    <style>
        :root { color-scheme: light dark; }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background-color: #e8e8e8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

        .header {
            background-color: #1e3a8a;
            padding: 24px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .header img { height: 44px; width: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 12px 0 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #cccccc;
        }

        .content > p { color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 16px; }

        .cancel-icon {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 52px;
            margin: 8px 0 20px;
        }

        .order-info {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 16px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .order-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .order-info p { margin: 6px 0; color: #333333; }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #777777;
            font-size: 12px;
            background-color: #e8e8e8;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body { background-color: #121212 !important; color: #e8e8e8 !important; }
            .wrapper { background-color: #121212; }
            .header { background-color: #1e3a8a !important; }
            .content { background-color: #1e1e1e !important; border-color: #333333 !important; }
            .content > p { color: #e0e0e0 !important; }
            .order-info { background-color: #2a2a2a !important; border-color: #3a3a3a !important; }
            .order-info h3 { color: #93c5fd !important; border-color: #3a3a3a !important; }
            .order-info p { color: #cccccc !important; }
            .footer { background-color: #121212 !important; color: #888888 !important; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Constru-ir" />
        <h1>Orden Cancelada</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="cancel-icon">❌</div>

        <p>Hola <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>Te informamos que tu orden ha sido cancelada.</p>

        <div class="order-info">
            <h3>Detalles de la Orden</h3>
            <p><strong>Número de Orden:</strong> {{orderNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Estado:</strong> Cancelada</p>
        </div>

        <p>Si tienes alguna pregunta o crees que esto fue un error, no dudes en contactarnos.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Este es un correo automático, por favor no respondas a este mensaje.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
